<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Sip" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Sip,</orth> to drink a small quantity and as if only with the lips: <bibl n="shak. shr 5.2.145" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. V, 2, 145</bibl>. With <emph>on</emph>: <cit><quote>s. on a cup,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 77</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>whereon but --ing,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.161" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 161</bibl></cit>. With <emph>to</emph>: <cit><quote>she would to each one s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 62</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>